#  DocMind — RAG Chatbot

> Upload any document and chat with it using AI. **100% Free** — no credit card needed.

---

##  Project Structure

```
DocMind/
├── app.py                        ← Entry point — run this!
├── requirements.txt              ← All dependencies
├── .env                          ← Your Groq API key                 ← Template for .env
├── .gitignore                    ← Keeps .env off GitHub
│
├── backend/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── document_processor.py     ← File loading + chunking + embeddings + FAISS
│   └── rag_chain.py              ← Groq LLM + retriever + prompt chain
│
└── frontend/
    ├── __init__.py
    ├── styles.py                 ← All custom CSS
    ├── sidebar.py                ← Sidebar UI + build knowledge base logic
    └── chat.py                   ← Chat messages + input box
```

---

##  How It Works

```
Upload Document
     ↓  backend/document_processor.py
     ↓  LangChain Loaders (PDF / TXT / DOCX / CSV)
Raw Text
     ↓  RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter
     ↓  chunk_size=1000, chunk_overlap=200
Chunks
     ↓  FastEmbedEmbeddings (BAAI/bge-small-en-v1.5)
     ↓  Runs locally — no API needed
Vectors
     ↓  FAISS Vector Store
Stored on your PC

Your Question
     ↓  backend/rag_chain.py
     ↓  FAISS similarity search → top k chunks
Relevant Context
     ↓  PromptTemplate → Groq LLM (LLaMA 3.3 70B)
Answer
     ↓  frontend/chat.py
Chat Interface ✅
```

