## 🚀 Setup & Run

### 1. Clone / Download the project
```
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/DocMind.git
cd DocMind
```

### 2. Install dependencies
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Create your `.env` file
```
# Copy the example
cp .env.example .env

# Edit .env and paste your Groq key
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_key_here
```
Get your **free** Groq key at [console.groq.com](https://console.groq.com)

### 4. Run the app
```
python -m streamlit run app.py
```

Open browser at `http://localhost:8501`

---

## 📖 Usage

1. App opens → you'll see ✅ **API Key loaded from .env file!**
2. **Upload documents** in the sidebar (PDF, TXT, DOCX, CSV)
3. Choose your **LLM model** and adjust sliders if needed
4. Click **🔨 Build Knowledge Base** — wait for processing
5. **Ask questions** in the chat box!

